    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just for the job. the job doesn't care about *me*. it just cares about the work. if the work gets done, the person doesn't matter. and if i just... stopped. if i just drifted away. it feels like the world would just keep spinning without even a hiccup. wouldn't it be easier for everyone if the ghost just finally disappeared?",
